nodes.text: Good Omen was an airship in the Ebon Fleet maintained by the Lost Tribe of Sith on Keshtah, a continent on the planet Kesh. The Grand Lord of the Tribe, Varner Hilts, rode aboard the Good Omen as it traversed the Western Sea to arrive at the continent of Alanciar. Upon disembarking, Hilts, dressed as the Keshiri deity the Bright Tuash, welcomed the Alanciari Keshiri into the Tribe and ended the invasion of Alanciar in peace.
